high_descs: Turn left, hang a right around the counter and walk to the counter ahead with the toaster.
Pick up the knife to the right of the toaster on the counter.
Turn left, hang a left at the stove and walk to the sink ahead.
Put the knife inside the sink to the right of the spoon, rinse it for a few seconds and pick it back up.
Turn around, walk towards the fridge, and turn around again to face the cabinets under the counter to the right of the sink.
Put the rinsed knife inside the far right drawer and close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed knife inside a drawer.

high_descs: Move around the left side of the island, go to the toaster on the counter.

Bring the knife to the the second drawer, right of the sink.
Put the knife in the right drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned knife in a drawer.
